           SHORT="GKSu is a library that provides a Gtk+ frontend to su and sudo. "
cat << EOF
GKSu is a library that provides a Gtk+ frontend to su and sudo. 
It supports login shells and preserving environment when acting 
as a su frontend. It is useful to menu items or other graphical 
programs that need to ask a user's password to run another 
program as another user. 
EOF
